query.sfwSql: SELECT * FROM SGT_WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST E WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN sgt_person p WITH(NOLOCK) on p.person_id = e.person_id inner join sgt_plan pl WITH(NOLOCK) on pl.plan_id = e.plan_id WHERE E.STATUS_VALUE <> 'FLTR'

SELECT YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE ) AS PAYMENT_YEAR,phh.payee_account_id, CAST(CAST(YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE) AS VARCHAR(4)) + '/' + '01' + '/01' AS DATETIME) as PaymentYearStartDate, dateadd(dd,-1,dateadd(yy,1,CAST(CAST(YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE) AS VARCHAR(4)) + '/' + '01' + '/01' AS DATETIME))) as PaymentYearEndDate, -- SUM(CASE WHEN CHECK_GROUP_CODE_VALUE = 'GRSS' -- THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS GROSS_AMOUNT, SUM(CASE WHEN PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION = 1 and PAYMENT_1099R_FLAG = 'Y' and VENDOR_FLAG= 'N' and ALLOW_ROLLOVER_CODE_VALUE <> 'CRET' and REISSUE_ITEMS_FLAG = 'N' THEN PHD.AMOUNT ELSE 0 END ) AS GROSS_AMOUNT, SUM(CASE WHEN CHECK_GROUP_CODE_VALUE = 'DEDT' and allow_rollover_code_value <> 'RRED' AND PHH.STATUS_VALUE <> 'CNLD' --Added 10268 THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS DEDUCTION_AMOUNT, -- SUM(CASE WHEN TAXABLE_ITEM_FLAG = 'Y' -- THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TAXABLE_AMOUNT, SUM(CASE WHEN PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION = 1 and PAYMENT_1099R_FLAG = 'Y' and VENDOR_FLAG= 'N' and TAXABLE_ITEM_FLAG = 'Y' and ALLOW_ROLLOVER_CODE_VALUE <> 'CRET' and REISSUE_ITEMS_FLAG = 'N' THEN PHD.AMOUNT ELSE 0 END ) AS TAXABLE_AMOUNT, SUM(CASE WHEN (ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION = 1 and PAYMENT_1099R_FLAG = 'Y' and VENDOR_FLAG= 'N' and TAXABLE_ITEM_FLAG <> 'Y' and ALLOW_ROLLOVER_CODE_VALUE <> 'CRET' and REISSUE_ITEMS_FLAG = 'N') THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS NonTaxable_Amount, SUM(ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION * AMOUNT ) AS NET_AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = @PAYEEACCOUNTID AND PHH.PAYMENT_DATE >= @GOLIVEDATE GROUP BY YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE ),phh.payee_account_id ORDER BY YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE ) DESC

select ORG.ORG_NAME as Employer_Org, ORG.ORG_CODE as Employer_Org_Code, PER.PERSON_ID as Perslink_id, (PER.last_name + ', ' + PER.first_name + ' ' +PER.MIDDLE_NAME) AS Person_Name, SP.PLAN_NAME as Plan_Name , CV.DESCRIPTION AS Level_Of_Coverage, REQ.CHANGE_EFFECTIVE_DATE as Effective_Change_Date ,PER.*,SP.*, REQ.* from SGT_WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST REQ WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN sgt_person_employment_detail DET WITH(NOLOCK) ON REQ.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID = DET.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID INNER JOIN sgt_person_employment EMP WITH(NOLOCK) ON EMP.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID = DET.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH(NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID = EMP.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG WITH(NOLOCK) ON ORG.ORG_ID = EMP.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGt_PLAN SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PLAN_ID = REQ.PLAN_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.SGT_WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV GHDV WITH(NOLOCK) ON GHDV.WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST_ID = REQ.WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV WITH(NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID = GHDV.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_ID AND GHDV.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE where EMP.org_id IN ( SELECT DISTINCT ORG.ORG_ID FROM SGT_ORG_CONTACT CNT WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_CONTACT CON WITH(NOLOCK) ON CON.CONTACT_ID = CNT.CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG WITH(NOLOCK) ON CNT.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID WHERE CNT.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' AND NDPERS_LOGIN_ID is null) and req.modified_date > isnull(@LastReportRunDate, '01/01/1900') and req.status_value = 'PSTD'

SELECT * INTO #TEMP1 FROM SGT_ENROLLMENT_DATA WHERE START_DATE=END_DATE AND PLAN_ID=19 AND EMPLOYER_ORG_ID=@ORGID UPDATE SGT_ENROLLMENT_DATA SET IS_BENEFIT_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED='Y' FROM SGT_ENROLLMENT_DATA ED INNER JOIN #TEMP1 T ON T.SOURCE_ID=ED.SOURCE_ID WHERE ED.ENROLLMENT_DATA_ID <= T.ENROLLMENT_DATA_ID DROP TABLE #TEMP1
SELECT * INTO #BenefitEnrlTEMP FROM ( --Enrolled and Waived plans SELECT DISTINCT ENRL.NDPERS_MEMBER_ID AS PERSON_ID, (ISNULL(PER.LAST_NAME, '') + ', ' + ISNULL(PER.FIRST_NAME, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(PER.MIDDLE_NAME, '')) AS PERSON_NAME, ENRL.SOURCE_ID, PER.DATE_OF_BIRTH, STUFF(RIGHT(ENRL.SSN,4), 1, 0, REPLICATE('X', 14 - LEN(ENRL.SSN))) AS SSN, ENRL.PEOPLESOFT_ID, ENRL.PLAN_ID, ENRL.Plan_Type, CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 18 THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE IS NULL AND HSA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HSA_ID = 0 THEN 'Non-NDPERS Insurance Pre-tax Premium' ELSE P.PLAN_NAME END ELSE P.PLAN_NAME END AS PLAN_NAME, P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE, CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_VALUE IS NULL THEN 'Waived' ELSE CV1.DESCRIPTION END AS PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS,
--Start Date CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID= 13 AND ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT IS NULL THEN LIFEH1.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE ELSE ENRL.START_DATE END AS START_DATE,
--END DATE CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID= 13 AND ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT IS NULL THEN LIFEH1.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE ELSE ENRL.END_DATE END AS END_DATE,
CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 19 THEN ISNULL( ENRL.PAY_PERIOD_AMOUNT,0.0) ELSE ENRL.PAY_PERIOD_AMOUNT END AS PAY_PERIOD_AMOUNT, ORG.ORG_NAME AS PROVIDER, CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_VALUE IN ('GFR1','HDHP','NGRF') THEN (SELECT SGS_CODE_VALUE.DESCRIPTION FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE SGS_CODE_VALUE.CODE_ID = 5010 AND SGS_CODE_VALUE.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_VALUE) ELSE CV2.DESCRIPTION END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID IN (30, 19) THEN ENRL.EMPLOYEE_EMPLOYER_MATCH ELSE CV2.DESCRIPTION END AS PLAN_OPTION, (CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN (SELECT DISTINCT TOP 1 SHORT_DESCRIPTION FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF WHERE COVERAGE_CODE = ENRL.COVERAGE_CODE_FOR_HEALTH) WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 18 AND ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE IS NULL AND HSA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HSA_ID > 0 THEN 'Monthly Health Savings Account' ELSE CV3.DESCRIPTION END) AS LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE, CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 18 AND ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT IS NULL THEN 0 WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 13 AND ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT IS NULL THEN LIFEH1.COVERAGE_AMOUNT ELSE ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT END AS COVERAGE_AMOUNT, (CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN NULL WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID != 12 AND ENRL.PRETAXED_PREMIUMS = 'Y' THEN 'Yes' WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID != 12 AND ENRL.PRETAXED_PREMIUMS = 'N' THEN 'No' END) AS PREMIUM_CONVERSION, ISNULL(ENRL.MONTHLY_PREMIUM,0.0) AS PREMIUM_AMOUNT, ENRL.CREATED_DATE AS POSTED_DATE, ENRL.IS_BENEFIT_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED, CASE WHEN ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_VALUE = 'LSPO' THEN 'Lump Sum Payout' WHEN (P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' AND ENRL.PLAN_ID != 30) OR ENRL.PLAN_ID = 14 THEN NULL WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 30 AND ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_VALUE != 'ADEC' THEN NULL ELSE CV4.DESCRIPTION END AS CHANGE_REASON, CV5.DESCRIPTION AS TYPE_VALUE FROM SGT_ENROLLMENT_DATA ENRL INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER ON PER.PERSON_ID = ENRL.NDPERS_MEMBER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN P ON P.PLAN_ID = ENRL.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ENRL.PROVIDER_ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV1 ON CV1.CODE_ID = ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_ID AND CV1.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_VALUE AND CV1.DATA2 = 'ERLD' LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV2 ON CV2.CODE_ID = ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_ID AND CV2.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV3 ON CV3.CODE_ID = ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_ID AND CV3.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV4 ON CV4.CODE_ID = ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_ID AND CV4.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV5 ON CV5.CODE_ID = ENRL.EMPLOYMENT_TYPE_ID AND CV5.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.EMPLOYMENT_TYPE_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HSA HSA ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = HSA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID --LIFE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY LIFEH1 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY WHERE EFFECTIVE_START_DATE != EFFECTIVE_END_DATE AND EFFECTIVE_START_DATE < ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE = ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_START_DATE DESC ) WHERE ENRL.EMPLOYER_ORG_ID = @ORGID AND ISNULL(ENRL.IS_BENEFIT_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED,'N') = 'N' AND (ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_VALUE in ('ENL1','ENL2','ENL3','ENL4') OR ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_VALUE IS NULL)
UNION
--SUSPENDED PLANS SELECT DISTINCT ENRL.NDPERS_MEMBER_ID AS PERSON_ID, (ISNULL(PER.LAST_NAME, '') + ', ' + ISNULL(PER.FIRST_NAME, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(PER.MIDDLE_NAME, '')) AS PERSON_NAME, ENRL.SOURCE_ID, PER.DATE_OF_BIRTH, STUFF(RIGHT(ENRL.SSN,4), 1, 0, REPLICATE('X', 14 - LEN(ENRL.SSN))) AS SSN, ENRL.PEOPLESOFT_ID, ENRL.PLAN_ID, ENRL.Plan_Type, --PLAN NAME CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 18 THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE IS NULL THEN 'Non-NDPERS Insurance Pre-tax Premium' ELSE P.PLAN_NAME END ELSE P.PLAN_NAME END AS PLAN_NAME, --BENEFIT TYPE P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE,
--PLAN PARTICIPATION STATUS CASE WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' THEN CASE WHEN PARH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND PARH1.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1' THEN 'Enrolled' WHEN PARH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND PARH2.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1' THEN 'Enrolled' END WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'INSR' THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID IN (12,16,17) THEN CASE WHEN GHDVH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND GHDVH1.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' THEN 'Enrolled' WHEN GHDVH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND GHDVH2.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' THEN 'Enrolled' END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 13 THEN CASE WHEN LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND LIFEH1.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' THEN 'Enrolled' WHEN LIFEH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND LIFEH2.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' THEN 'Enrolled' END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 14 THEN CASE WHEN EAPH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND EAPH1.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' THEN 'Enrolled' WHEN EAPH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND EAPH2.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' THEN 'Enrolled' END END WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'DEFF' THEN CV1.DESCRIPTION WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'FLEX' THEN CASE WHEN FCH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND FCH1.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL4' THEN 'Enrolled' WHEN FCH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID > 0 AND FCH2.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL4' THEN 'Enrolled' END END AS PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS,
-- START DATE CASE WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' THEN CASE WHEN PARH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN PARH1.START_DATE WHEN PARH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN PARH2.START_DATE END WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'INSR' THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID IN (12,16,17) THEN CASE WHEN GHDVH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN GHDVH1.START_DATE WHEN GHDVH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN GHDVH2.START_DATE END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 13 THEN CASE WHEN LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN LIFEH1.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE WHEN LIFEH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN LIFEH2.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 14 THEN CASE WHEN EAPH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN EAPH1.START_DATE WHEN EAPH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN EAPH2.START_DATE END END WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'DEFF' THEN ENRL.START_DATE WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'FLEX' THEN CASE WHEN FCH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN FCH1.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE WHEN FCH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN FCH2.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE END END AS START_DATE,
--END DATE CASE WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' THEN CASE WHEN PARH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN PARH1.END_DATE WHEN PARH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN PARH2.END_DATE END WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'INSR' THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID IN (12,16,17) THEN CASE WHEN GHDVH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN GHDVH1.END_DATE WHEN GHDVH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN GHDVH2.END_DATE END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 13 THEN CASE WHEN LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN LIFEH1.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE WHEN LIFEH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN LIFEH2.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 14 THEN CASE WHEN EAPH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN EAPH1.END_DATE WHEN EAPH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN EAPH2.END_DATE END END WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'DEFF' THEN ENRL.END_DATE WHEN P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'FLEX' THEN CASE WHEN FCH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN FCH1.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE WHEN FCH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID > 0 THEN FCH2.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE END END AS END_DATE,
CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 19 THEN ISNULL( ENRL.PAY_PERIOD_AMOUNT,0.0) ELSE ENRL.PAY_PERIOD_AMOUNT END AS PAY_PERIOD_AMOUNT, ORG.ORG_NAME AS PROVIDER, CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_VALUE IN ('GFR1','HDHP','NGRF') THEN (SELECT SGS_CODE_VALUE.DESCRIPTION FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE SGS_CODE_VALUE.CODE_ID = 5010 AND SGS_CODE_VALUE.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_VALUE) ELSE CV2.DESCRIPTION END WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID IN (30, 19) THEN ENRL.EMPLOYEE_EMPLOYER_MATCH ELSE CV2.DESCRIPTION END AS PLAN_OPTION, (CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN (SELECT DISTINCT TOP 1 SHORT_DESCRIPTION FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN_GROUP_HEALTH_MEDICARE_PART_D_COVERAGE_REF WHERE COVERAGE_CODE = ENRL.COVERAGE_CODE_FOR_HEALTH) ELSE CV3.DESCRIPTION END) AS LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE, CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 18 AND ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE ENRL.COVERAGE_AMOUNT END, (CASE WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN NULL WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID != 12 AND ENRL.PRETAXED_PREMIUMS = 'Y' THEN 'Yes' WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID != 12 AND ENRL.PRETAXED_PREMIUMS = 'N' THEN 'No' END) AS PREMIUM_CONVERSION, ISNULL(ENRL.MONTHLY_PREMIUM,0.0) AS PREMIUM_AMOUNT, ENRL.CREATED_DATE AS POSTED_DATE, ENRL.IS_BENEFIT_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED, CASE WHEN ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_VALUE = 'LSPO' THEN 'Lump Sum Payout' WHEN (P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' AND ENRL.PLAN_ID != 30) OR ENRL.PLAN_ID = 14 THEN NULL WHEN ENRL.PLAN_ID = 30 AND ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_VALUE != 'ADEC' THEN NULL ELSE CV4.DESCRIPTION END AS CHANGE_REASON, CV5.DESCRIPTION AS TYPE_VALUE FROM SGT_ENROLLMENT_DATA ENRL INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER ON PER.PERSON_ID = ENRL.NDPERS_MEMBER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN P ON P.PLAN_ID = ENRL.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ENRL.PROVIDER_ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV1 ON CV1.CODE_ID = ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_ID AND CV1.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.PLAN_STATUS_VALUE AND CV1.DATA2 in ( 'SPND', 'CNLD') LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV2 ON CV2.CODE_ID = ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_ID AND CV2.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.PLAN_OPTION_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV3 ON CV3.CODE_ID = ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_ID AND CV3.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.LEVEL_OF_COVERAGE_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV4 ON CV4.CODE_ID = ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_ID AND CV4.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.CHANGE_REASON_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV5 ON CV5.CODE_ID = ENRL.EMPLOYMENT_TYPE_ID AND CV5.CODE_VALUE = ENRL.EMPLOYMENT_TYPE_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY PARH1 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PARH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID --RETIREMENT AND PARH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID IN ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY WHERE START_DATE != END_DATE AND START_DATE < ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY START_DATE DESC )
LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY PARH2 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PARH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND PARH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID IN ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY WHERE START_DATE <= ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY START_DATE DESC )
--GHDV LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV GHDV ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY GHDVH1 ON GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = GHDVH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID AND GHDVH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID = ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY WHERE START_DATE != END_DATE AND START_DATE < ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID ORDER BY START_DATE DESC )
LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY GHDVH2 ON GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = GHDVH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID AND GHDVH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID = ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY WHERE START_DATE <= ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID ORDER BY START_DATE DESC ) --LIFE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY LIFEH1 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND LIFEH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY WHERE EFFECTIVE_START_DATE != EFFECTIVE_END_DATE AND EFFECTIVE_START_DATE < ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_START_DATE DESC )
LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY LIFEH2 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = LIFEH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND LIFEH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_LIFE_HISTORY WHERE EFFECTIVE_START_DATE <= ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_START_DATE DESC ) --FLEX LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY FCH1 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = FCH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND FCH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID = ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY WHERE EFFECTIVE_START_DATE != EFFECTIVE_END_DATE AND EFFECTIVE_START_DATE < ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL4' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_START_DATE DESC)
LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY FCH2 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = FCH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND FCH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID = ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLEX_COMP_HISTORY WHERE EFFECTIVE_START_DATE <= ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL4' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY EFFECTIVE_START_DATE DESC) --EAP LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY EAPH1 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = EAPH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND EAPH1.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID = ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY WHERE START_DATE != END_DATE AND START_DATE < ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY START_DATE DESC)
LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY EAPH2 ON ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = EAPH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND EAPH2.PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID = ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EAP_HISTORY WHERE START_DATE <= ENRL.START_DATE AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = ENRL.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY START_DATE DESC)
WHERE ENRL.EMPLOYER_ORG_ID = @ORGID AND ISNULL(ENRL.IS_BENEFIT_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED,'N') = 'N' ) A

union
